data.description: 72HOUR HOME SALE! Come and see your new FULLY FURNISHED home in Golf Knolls! This spacious, open-concept home offers an exceptional living experience. With a FENCED YARD, one of the LARGEST LOTS in the neighborhood, a large BONUS BUILDING and a WHEELCHAIR LIFT, there are so many possibilities!  The ROOF is NEW, there is FRESH PAINT IN AND OUT, and all the FURNITURE AND APPLIANCES are INCLUDED. All you need to do is move in and make it yours. Ask about the assumable loan, too!
